mobiheader.fullname: Learn You Some Erlang For Great Good!

exthheader.author: Fred Hebert
exthheader.description: Learn You Some Erlang for Great Good! is a hilariously illustrated guide to the concurrent functional programming language. As you laugh along with Hebert’s brilliantly quirky drawings, you’ll effortlessly pick up this complex language and have fun while you’re at it..
